{"id":170,"ayahs":[{"number":156,"arabic":"۞ وَٱكْتُبْ لَنَا فِى هَٰذِهِ ٱلدُّنْيَا حَسَنَةًۭ وَفِى ٱلْءَاخِرَةِ إِنَّا هُدْنَآ إِلَيْكَ ۚ قَالَ عَذَابِىٓ أُصِيبُ بِهِۦ مَنْ أَشَآءُ ۖ وَرَحْمَتِى وَسِعَتْ كُلَّ شَىْءٍۢ ۚ فَسَأَكْتُبُهَا لِلَّذِينَ يَتَّقُونَ وَيُؤْتُونَ ٱلزَّكَوٰةَ وَٱلَّذِينَ هُم بِـَٔايَٰتِنَا يُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"And ordain Thou for us what is good in this world as well as in the life to come: behold, unto Thee have we turned in repentance!\" [God] answered: \"With My chastisement do I afflict whom I will - but My grace overspreads everything: and so I shall confer it on those who are conscious of Me and spend in charity, and who believe in Our messages-","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1110.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":81235,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ وَٱكْتُبْ","translation":"এবং লিখে দিন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_156_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81236,"position":2,"arabic":"لَنَا","translation":"জন্যে আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_156_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81237,"position":3,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_156_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81238,"position":4,"arabic":"هَـٰذِهِ","translation":"এই","audioUrl":"wbw/007_156_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81239,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلدُّنْيَا","translation":"পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_156_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81240,"position":6,"arabic":"حَسَنَةًۭ","translation":"কল্যাণ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_156_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81241,"position":7,"arabic":"وَفِى","translation":"ও মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_156_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81242,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْـَٔاخِرَةِ","translation":"আখেরাতে (কল্যাণ)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_156_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81243,"position":9,"arabic":"إِنَّا","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_156_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81244,"position":10,"arabic":"هُدْنَآ","translation":"প্রত্যাবর্ত