"translation":"অতএব যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_157_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81424,"position":32,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","translation":"ঈমান আনে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_157_033.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81425,"position":33,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"উপর তার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_157_034.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81426,"position":34,"arabic":"وَعَزَّرُوهُ","translation":"ও সম্মান করে তাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_157_035.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81427,"position":35,"arabic":"وَنَصَرُوهُ","translation":"ও তারা সাহায্য করে তাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_157_036.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81428,"position":36,"arabic":"وَٱتَّبَعُوا۟","translation":"এবং অনুসরণ করে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_157_037.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81429,"position":37,"arabic":"ٱلنُّورَ","translation":"আলোর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_157_038.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81430,"position":38,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِىٓ","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_157_039.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81431,"position":39,"arabic":"أُنزِلَ","translation":"নামানো হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_157_040.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81432,"position":40,"arabic":"مَعَهُۥٓ ۙ","translation":"সাথে তার","audioUrl":"wbw/007_157_041.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81434,"position":41,"arabic":"أُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ","translation":"ঐসব লোক","audioUrl":"wbw/007_157_043.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81435,"position":42,"arabic":"هُمُ","translation":"তারাই","audioUrl":"wbw/007_157_044.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81436,"position":43,"arabic":"ٱلْمُفْلِحُونَ","translation":"সফলকাম\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_157_045.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81437,"position":44,"arabic":"١٥٧","translation":"(১৫৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":158,"arabic":"قُلْ يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلنَّاسُ إِنِّى رَسُولُ ٱللَّهِ إِلَيْكُمْ جَمِيعًا ٱلَّذِى لَهُۥ مُلْكُ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضِ ۖ لَآ إِلَٰهَ إِلَّا هُوَ يُحْىِۦ وَيُمِيتُ ۖ فَـَٔامِنُوا۟ بِٱللَّهِ وَرَسُولِهِ ٱلنَّبِىِّ ٱلْأُمِّىِّ ٱلَّذِى يُؤْمِنُ بِٱللَّهِ وَكَلِمَٰتِهِۦ وَٱتَّبِعُوهُ لَعَلَّكُمْ تَهْتَدُونَ","translation":"Say [O Muhammad]: \"O mankind! Verily, I am an apostle of God to all of you, [sent by Him] unto whom the dominion over the heavens and the earth belongs! There is no deity save Him; He [alone] grants life and deals death!\" Believe, then, in God and His Apostle-the unlettered Prophet who believes in God and His words-and follow him, so that you might find guidance!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1112.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":81482,"position":1,"arabic":"قُلْ","translation":"বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_158_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81483,"position":2,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","translation":"\"হে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_158_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81484,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلنَّاسُ","translation":"\"মানবমন্ডলী","audioUrl":"wbw/007_158_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81485,"position":4,"arabic":"إِنِّى","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই আমি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_158_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81486,"position":5,"arabic":"رَسُولُ","translation":"রাসূল","audioUrl":"wbw/007_158_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81487,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_158_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81488,"position":7,"arabic":"إِلَيْكُمْ","translation":"প্রতি তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_158_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81489,"position":8,"arabic":"جَمِيعًا","translation":"সকলের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_158_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81490,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","translation":"যিনি (এমন যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_158_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81491,"position":10,"arabic":"لَهُۥ","translation":"জন্যে তাঁরই (রয়েছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_158_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81492,"position":11,"arabic":"مُلْكُ","translation":"সার্বভৌমত্ব","audioUrl":"wbw/007_158_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81493,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلسَّ